{
  "stem": "9156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The man that I married-- which was not a real marriage, I hope that's clear-- was Wilhelm Kuhn, K-U-H-N.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought he was very decent in doing that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I let him know that, but I said, 'Don't ever touch me.' And that just-- I just couldn't take that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he understood that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't have-- he could go to Vienna first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have to live together because this other friend, who also went through the same thing as I, said we do have to live together for a while.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how we explained it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Her husband lived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we said my husband hasn't yet found an apartment or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we lived in another-- so we never lived together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I did see him a few times, yes, in Vienna, and then later, you know, in Paris, much later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I felt that I wanted to have it clear that we were divorced.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we got a divorce on grounds of that he is not Jewish and I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the Nazis would give that very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know the year, but it is before I entered the United States, which was very good because I didn't have to go under Kuhn to the United States.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got under my maiden name to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Vienna-- and I want to make that faster because I'm afraid I will never get through with this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was very poor, people were singing wonderful songs, but in the street corners to get a few pennies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I, as usual, could do something by-- give me the word again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tutoring.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's the matter with me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That word gets away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All right, by tutoring.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
